OL,4,CUniversal basic income: Wales' trial
OL,5,C'should include everyone'
OL,6, Supporters of universal basic income
OL,7, have called for a trial in Wales to
OL,8, include everyone living in a test area.
OL,10,FUBI pays everyone a fixed sum,
OL,11,Fregardless of their circumstances.
OL,13,FThe Welsh government has said its small
OL,14,Ftrial could involve people leaving the
OL,15,Fcare system.
OL,17,FIn an open letter to the first
OL,18,Fminister, signatories, including the
OL,19,Ffuture generations commissioner, said
OL,20,Fit needed to cover geographical areas
OL,21,Ffor it to be an effective test.
